{"tid":1072610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[同情分負分]新殖民婦涉要求「打尖」不遂襲護士 官：已經忙到一頭煙仲要遇到刁民","createTime":"2019-03-22T06:33:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-22T07:18:44.000Z","uid":51271,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0ef79d306cde2ca38dea4d0f82e3f8fd01ddb3f6","tid":1072610,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T06:33:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190322/59398269\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190322%2F59398269&d=nGD0VYfdVRVKlmm%2FccroE%2FrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=55bcfcae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190322%2F59398269&h=81a0c331\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190322/59398269</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去年6月才取得單程證來港的新移民婦人，今年初帶耳痛10歲兒子到廣華醫院急症室求診，其間疑不滿等候多時不獲治理，要求「打尖」讓兒子先看醫生，更擅闖診療室。護士見狀阻止，爭執期間婦人疑推跌護士，被控普通襲擊罪，案件今日提堂。主任裁判官吳蕙芳庭上對肇事婦人直言：「人哋已經忙到一頭煙，仲要遇到刁民攪攪震！」婦人暫時毋須答辯，案件押後至下月24日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n案件今在九龍城裁判法院提訊，操普通話的被告辜建芬（41歲），被控一項普通襲擊罪。控罪指她於今年1月29日在廣華醫院急症室襲擊女子羅錦霞。<br />\n<br />\n辯方申請毋須答辯並押後案件，以待索取檢控文件及向被告提供法律意見。辯方透露，被告去年6月才取得單程證從四川來港，任職侍應，與丈夫育有一名10歲兒子。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>主任裁判官吳蕙芳指被告涉嫌襲擊護士，直言在醫院發生暴力事件非常嚴重，而本案比一般襲擊案更嚴重：「人哋已經忙到一頭煙，仲要遇到刁民攪攪震！」<br />\n<br />\n吳官及後用普通話對被告說：「你還要在一個孩子面前打人，誰教你的？」被告聞言落淚，吳官見狀即謂：「你還要在我法庭哭呀？來我法庭沒有同情分，眼淚是沒有同情分的。」案件最終押後至下月24日，屆時才聽取被告答辯。被告續准以500元保釋候訊。</strong><br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：KCCC846/19】<br />\n記者楊思雅"},{"pid":"ed335ad2862bfd18d5b2bb6e2483e1f14234b689","tid":1072610,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T06:34:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190322/large/1553235215_74c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190322%2Flarge%2F1553235215_74c8.jpg&h=d8260032&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n被告辜建芬。楊思雅攝(蘋果日報)"},{"pid":"83ebccb9270951e6f214e2b33840aa8b7bf0a959","tid":1072610,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T07:08:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7114584ec6d668770bcbc98831baddf0ddc2cb89","tid":1072610,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T07:11:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">主任裁判官吳蕙芳</span></span>"},{"pid":"61be5eede317299892e64ad2bd20be46667757aa","tid":1072610,"uid":34949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T07:11:33.000Z","msg":"死支那婦，屌你老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a2ee36f89c55b4be2af7858f8d303ccef6a1f94","tid":1072610,"uid":128600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T07:14:01.000Z","msg":"打尖坐監啦"},{"pid":"c5bb77c4c8e9c7019bce256ac338022edc8e09ab","tid":1072610,"uid":78349,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"7114584ec6d668770bcbc98831baddf0ddc2cb89","tid":1072610,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T07:11:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">主任裁判官吳蕙芳</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T07:18:44.000Z","msg":"佢次次鬧人都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上次個打電話呀婆 佢問個呀婆你係咪傻架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}